---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TopAppBar from '../components/TopAppBar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Nelsibeth Oliva - Architecting Odoo Solutions">
    <TopAppBar />
    
    <main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center mb-32">
            <div class="lg:col-span-7">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high border border-outline-variant/15 mb-6">
                    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary animate-pulse"></span>
                    <span class="text-xs font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-primary">Disponible para Proyectos</span>
                </div>
                <h1 class="font-headline text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-6 leading-tight">
                    Arquitecto de Soluciones <span class="hero-gradient bg-clip-text text-transparent">Odoo</span>.
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mb-10 leading-relaxed font-body">
                    Desarrollador Técnico Sr. especializado en implementaciones de Odoo a medida, automatización con Python y estructuras de bases de datos PostgreSQL escalables.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 font-headline">
                    <button class="hero-gradient text-on-primary font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-2 group transition-all">
                        Hablemos 
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" translate="no">arrow_forward</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="px-8 py-4 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/30 text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors">
                        Ver Casos de Estudio Técnicos
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative">
                <div class="aspect-square relative rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden group">
                    <img 
                        alt="Nelsibeth Oliva" 
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" 
                        data-alt="Professional studio portrait of a confident developer with vibrant blue hair highlights, dramatic cinematic lighting, deep sapphire background" 
                        src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuD47BwGGyAJCXoemPsEvaXiqUIL9XSxvPC30av2nquJo413Hbt0CSbqTqaOO7K4cGcbD2QWQamrooVbuWzAukG1hH_8CBIp2-ZFYS0O0QV-xnY6ThfZQRvJPVqauJCuqSglwvnPa2Jjy43P8BB2g5vwvd7wtMfE1XI0eDgEQUZ8Yf6ztxg18mz0xD00xFde414jD2aQXLecVHcmCebN0U8cplafP94xnOX1P7TNzdZC-pyloit8uqU77DyE1UhD6FVzt27ECYMBeBd1"
                    />
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background via-transparent to-transparent opacity-60"></div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Floating Card -->
                <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 p-6 bg-surface-container-high/80 backdrop-blur-xl border border-outline-variant/15 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl max-w-xs xl:left-[-2rem]">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-3">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" translate="no" data-weight="fill">terminal</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-xs font-label text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-tighter">Estado del Stack</p>
                            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-on-surface font-headline">Certificado V17</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="h-1.5 w-full bg-surface-container rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="h-full w-[95%] hero-gradient"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Professional Summary & Expertise -->
        <section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-24 items-start mb-32">
            <div>
                <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
                    Resumen Profesional
                    <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-outline-variant/15"></span>
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-6 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-lg font-body">
                    <p>
                        Con más de 6 años de experiencia enfocada en el <span class="text-primary font-semibold">ecosistema Odoo</span>, cierro la brecha entre los requisitos comerciales complejos y la arquitectura técnica de alto rendimiento.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Mi enfoque prioriza la mantenibilidad y la escalabilidad, asegurando que los módulos personalizados se integren sin problemas con el núcleo de Odoo mientras brindan la flexibilidad necesaria para los flujos de trabajo empresariales en evolución.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div>
                <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
                    Experticia Principal
                    <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-outline-variant/15"></span>
                </h2>
                
                <!-- Bento Grid Style Expertise -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <div class="col-span-2 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/10 hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors group">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl" translate="no" data-weight="fill">rocket_launch</span>
                            <span class="text-xs font-label text-slate-500">Dominio</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl mb-1">Odoo Enterprise</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Experto en el framework, especialista en ORM y personalizador de UI/UX para diversos sectores industriales.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/10 hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-variant flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" translate="no" data-weight="fill">code</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-1">Python</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant font-body">Lógica de backend, scripts de automatización e integraciones de alto nivel.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/10 hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-variant flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" translate="no" data-weight="fill">database</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-1">PostgreSQL</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant font-body">Consultas avanzadas, optimización de bases de datos y gestión de migraciones.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Stats / Proof Points -->
        <section class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 py-16 border-y border-outline-variant/10">
            <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-4xl font-headline font-black text-primary mb-1">45+</p>
                <p class="text-xs font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">Módulos Desplegados</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-4xl font-headline font-black text-primary mb-1">12</p>
                <p class="text-xs font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">Migraciones Globales</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-4xl font-headline font-black text-primary mb-1">98%</p>
                <p class="text-xs font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">Récord de Uptime</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-4xl font-headline font-black text-primary mb-1">6años</p>
                <p class="text-xs font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">Liderazgo Técnico</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Layout>
